divs: sighting detailsbecause of recent ufo reports\sightings in the land o' lakes, fl area i have been paying attention to the sky more than i normally would. sometimes i take photos randomly just to see if i might capture something on film. other times i take photos when something catches my eye. the attached photos (reg. and crop\zoom) show a star-like object that appears to be "shooting" upward. the object also appears to have a solid body object directly below the light. i do not believe it is a star because the light is relatively close and my digital camera does not feature a zoom powerful enough to photograph stars. the star-like object is not featured in the frames previous to or following the one particular shot that captured the light. obviously i'm not an expert, but i do find the photo to be rather curious.
